- @body_id = 'home'
%title
  Home | Caption Monster

.jumbotron
  .home-title
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        %h1
          CaPTioN MoNSTeR
        %h2
          Create and share captions
    .row
      .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
        %p
          Caption Monster was designed to be a fun place to create picture captions. You can upload images, write captions and vote on their favorite captions. Upload a picture and see what crazy captions others come up with or create your own.
.container#view-caption-container
  .row.home-options
    .col-md-6
      %h2 
        Create an Image
        %br
        %small
          Get started by uploading your own image and creating a caption for it. Then watch as other users also post captions and vote on their favorites. Will your caption win?
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          %a{:href => new_entry_path}
            %button.btn.btn-primary
              Get Started
    .col-md-6
      %h2
        Create Captions
        %br
        %small
          Don't feel like posting your own image? No problem, browse from images already uploaded. Create your own caption or vote for other user's captions.
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          .btn-group
            %button.btn.btn-primary.dropdown-toggle{:type => "button", "data-toggle" => "dropdown"}
              Find Captions
              %span.caret
            %ul.dropdown-menu{:role => "menu"}
              %li
                = link_to "Random Image", random_entry_path(:id)
              %li
                = link_to "Recent Images", entries_index_path
              %li
                = link_to "Recent Captions", captions_index_path
              %li
                = link_to "Most Popular", popular_entry_path(:id)